<i>adjective</i>: 힘들다 [힘들다], 힘겹다 [힘겹따] <i>verb</i>: 힘들어지다 [힘드러지다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>힘들다 [힘들다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. strenuous; laborious</dd><br>
<dd>힘이 많이 쓰이는 면이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Requiring much power or effort.</dd><br>
<dd>2. hard; difficult; tough</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 하는 것이 어렵거나 곤란하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Difficult or tough to do a certain act.</dd><br>
<dd>3. badly off; in trouble; in difficulty</dd><br>
<dd>상황이나 형편이 넉넉하지 않고 곤란하다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's financial sitution or circumstance being in trouble or not being favorable.</dd><br>
<dd>4. hard; difficult</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 쓰이거나 수고가 되는 면이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Requiring much attention and effort.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>힘겹다 [힘겹따]</dt><br>
<dd>difficult; tough; painstaking; strenuous</dd><br>
<dd>힘이 모자라거나 부족하여 어떤 일을 당해 내기 어렵다.</dd><br>
<dd>Difficulty coping with a certain task due to lack of energy or power.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>힘들어지다 [힘드러지다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. strenuous; laborious</dd><br>
<dd>힘이 많이 쓰이는 면이 생기다.</dd><br>
<dd>Requiring much more power or effort than before.</dd><br>
<dd>2. harder; more difficult; tougher</dd><br>
<dd>전보다 어렵거나 곤란하게 되다.</dd><br>
<dd>More difficult or tougher to do a certain act than before.</dd><br>
<dd>3. becoming hard; becoming difficult</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 쓰이거나 애를 쓰게 되는 부분이 생기다.</dd><br>
<dd>Requiring much more attention and effort than before.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>